title: Press Release: Bills Signed: H.J.Res. 62, H.J.Res. 63, H.J.Res. 64 | The White House
content: On Thursday, December 21, 2023, the President signed into law:H.J.Res. 62, which reappoints Michael Govan as a citizen regent of the Board of Regents of the Smithsonian Institution;H.J.Res. 63, which appoints Antoinette Bush as a citizen regent of the Board of Regents of the Smithsonian Institution; andH.J.Res. 64, which reappoints Roger W. Ferguson as a citizen regent of the Board of Regents of the Smithsonian Institution.###
